                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Favonius Bladework"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Deals 3<span style=\"color: #80FFD7\"> Anemo DMG</span>, the target is forcibly switched to the next character.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/04/248396185/f21a21302c39df14caac1bbc0a6bef40_4255822343333059072.png",
                "id": "talent78526",
                "key": "Gale Blade",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Gale Blade"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Heals all your characters for 2 HP, summons 1 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Dandelion Field</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/04/248396185/06d120531fd7d61a928bac235bbaeed2_8982292293945511190.png",
                "id": "talent33201",
                "key": "Dandelion Breeze",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 4,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Dandelion Breeze"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Summon</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">End Phase</span>: Deal 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo DMG</span>, heal your active character for 1 HP.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s): 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/12/35428890/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_608716659917144802.png",
                "id": "talent42161",
                "key": "Dandelion Field",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/12/35428890/9138f4f0e38e85d3c4e035bdf2025636_7708051339461539636.png",
                "title": "Dandelion Field"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Reacts with Elements if they are already applied:<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Cryo Swirl</span>: Deals 1 Cryo DMG to all opposing chracters except the target<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Hydro Swirl:</span> Deals 1 Hydro DMG to all opposing characters except the target<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Pyro Swirl</span>: Deals 1 Pyro DMG to all opposing characters except the target<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Electro Swirl</span>: Deals 1 Electro DMG to all opposing characters except the target</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/12/35428890/c97292d96456bfe4abeca16bfce801e4_8580553735029498706.png",
                "id": "talent53746",
                "key": "Anemo DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Anemo DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Physical DMG</span></strong></p><p>Physical DMG will not apply any Elements, nor can it engage in Elemental Reactions.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Usage(s)</span></strong></p><p>After this card's effect is triggered, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage </span>of it will be consumed.</p><p>This card will be discarded immediately once it has 0 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usages </span>remaining.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/15/35428890/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_598968431637697893.png",
